# claude-harness-portable: 셸/JS 스크립트는 LF 고정 — Windows 체크아웃에서도 bash 가 \r 없이 동작.
claude-harness-portable/**/*.sh   text eol=lf
claude-harness-portable/**/*.js   text eol=lf
claude-harness-portable/**/*.md   text eol=lf
claude-harness-portable/**/*.txt  text eol=lf
claude-harness-portable/**/*.tmpl text eol=lf
